          externalId: 'src:bada-miller-reanalysis-2008',
          name: 'Johnson A.P., Cleaves H.J., Dworkin J.P., Glavin D.P., Lazcano A., Bada J.L. The Miller Volcanic Spark Discharge Experiment. Science 2008;322(5900):404.',
